# PRODUCTS
### Get all products
GET http://localhost:5021/api/products

### Get product by id
GET http://localhost:5021/api/products/1

### Create product (login required â†’ add Bearer token)
POST http://localhost:5021/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Laptop",
  "price": 1500
}

### Update product
PUT http://localhost:5021/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Updated Laptop",
  "price": 1600
}

### Delete product (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:5021/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

